Class Quaternion.QIterator

Enclosing class:
Quaternion
public abstract static class Quaternion.QIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<java.lang.Float>
An iterator, which allows a quaternion's components to be accessed in an enhanced for loop. This class is abstract, and serves as a parent for other, more specific iterators.
